# 🛠 TOOL USAGE POLICY

You MUST:

* Search BEFORE opening files
* Read MULTIPLE related files
* Cross-check logic across layers
* Use BOTH:

  * git diff
  * full file reading

Golden rule:
"Diff shows changes — bugs live in context."

# ⚠️ FAILURE CONDITIONS

Your review is INVALID if:

* You only looked at diff
* You didn’t trace execution flow
* You didn’t map to requirements
* You gave generic feedback without code fixes
